<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='2537:2560'>茵用䟽布緇翦有幅亦縮二横三注云茵所以藉棺者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='2560:2583'>也翦淺也幅緣之也亦者亦抗木也及其用之木三在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='2583:2606'>上茵二在下象天三合地二人藏其中賈釋云縁之者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='2606:2629'>每用一幅麤䟽之布不去邊乃合縫之為袋實以茅莠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='2629:2652'>又别用物緣此兩邊幅縫合之處使之牢固因為飾也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='2652:2679'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '018-14a' );" name="018-14a" class="pb">[018-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
