<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='2730:2753'>既夕禮云苞二所以裹奠羊豕之肉也下記云葦苞長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='2753:2776'>三尺一編以此羊豕之肉即遣奠所苞牲之下體也又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='2776:2799'>註云用便易者謂以葦長難用截取三尺一道編之用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='2799:2808'>苞牲體為便易也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='2808:2835'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '018-15a' );" name="018-15a" class="pb">[018-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
