<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='3724:3747'>既夕禮云筲三黍稷麥註云筲畚種類也其容蓋與簋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='3747:3770'>同一觳也賈釋云畚器所以盛種此筲與畚盛種同類</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='3770:3797'>故舉為況也又下記云菅筲三其實皆瀹<span class='krp-note'>音/藥</span>註云米麥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='3797:3818'>皆湛之以湯未知神之所享不用食道所以為敬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='3818:3845'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '018-19a' );" name="018-19a" class="pb">[018-19a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
