<span class='tline' id='l360' data-llen='5439:5466'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '018-26b' );" name="018-26b" class="pb">[018-26b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l361' data-llen='5466:5489'>君即位而為椑歳一漆之若未成然鄭又云椑謂杝棺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l362' data-llen='5489:5512'>親尸者椑堅著之言也言天子椑内又有水兕革棺喪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l363' data-llen='5512:5535'>大記曰君大棺八寸屬六寸椑四寸上大夫大棺八寸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l364' data-llen='5535:5558'>屬六寸下大夫大棺六寸屬四寸士棺六寸註云大棺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l365' data-llen='5558:5581'>棺之在表者也檀弓曰天子之棺四重水兕革棺被之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l366' data-llen='5581:5622'>各厚三寸<span class='krp-note'>合六寸此/為一重</span>杝棺一<span class='krp-note'>杝棺木所/謂椑棺也</span>梓棺二<span class='krp-note'>屬與大/棺也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l367' data-llen='5622:5645'>四者皆周此從内説而出也然則大棺及屬皆用梓椑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l368' data-llen='5645:5668'>用杝以是差之上公革棺不被三重也諸侯無革棺再</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l369' data-llen='5668:5695'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '018-27a' );" name="018-27a" class="pb">[018-27a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l370' data-llen='5695:5718'>重也大夫無椑一重也士無屬不重也庶人之棺四寸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l371' data-llen='5718:5737'>棺束縮二横三祍每束一<span class='krp-note'>祍今/小要</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l372' data-llen='5737:5764'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '018-28a' );" name="018-28a" class="pb">[018-28a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
